What it can?
==========

Simple wrapper around maim and xclip for doing screenshots
Call `lumes -h` for information

Capabilities
-----------

1. Selection area
2. Move screen to clipboard (by default)
3. Save screenshot in file or in catalogs

Requirements
----------

1. maim
2. xclip


